graph LR
    Start([Authentication module start]) --> Login[Input Credentials<br/>Username/Password]
    Login --> Valid{Credentials<br/>Valid?}

%% If credentials fail
    Valid -- N --> End([Authentication module end])

%% If credentials pass
    Valid -- Y --> GenJWT[Generate JWT<br/>Sign with Secret]
    GenJWT --> SaveSession[Store/Update Session<br/>in Database/Redis]
    SaveSession --> Success{Success?}

%% Loop back if DB update fails or retry is needed
    Success -- N --> GenJWT

%% Finish
    Success -- Y --> Return[Return JWT to Client]
    Return --> End